    <title>文章测试</title>
    <link href="/2023/02/21/%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/"/>
    <url>/2023/02/21/%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>图片测试<br><img src="/img/105371106_p0.jpg"></p><p>公式测试</p><h1 id="定积分的求法"><a href="#定积分的求法" class="headerlink" title="定积分的求法"></a>定积分的求法</h1><p>运用基本性质: 如可加（找出有限个间断点），交换上下限</p><h2 id="变量代换法"><a href="#变量代换法" class="headerlink" title="变量代换法"></a>变量代换法</h2><blockquote><p> &#x3D;&#x3D;重要性质&#x3D;&#x3D;:$f(x)$在$[0,1]$连续,</p><p>$$\begin{aligned} \int_0^{\pi&#x2F;2} f(\sin x)dx&amp;&#x3D;\int_0^{\pi&#x2F;2} f(\cos x)dx  \\int_0^{\pi} xf(\sin x)dx&amp;&#x3D;\frac{\pi}{2}\int_0^{\pi} f(\sin x)dx \end{aligned}$$</p></blockquote><p>证明:(1) 令$t&#x3D;\frac{\pi}{2}-x$</p><p>(2) 令$t&#x3D;\pi-x$</p><blockquote><p>$\int_{0}^\pi xf(\sin x)dx&#x3D;\pi\int_0^{\pi}f(\sin x)dx-\int_{0}^\pi xf(\sin x)dx$</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>例 $\int_{0}^{\pi&#x2F;2}\frac{x\sin x}{1+\cos^2x}&#x3D;\frac{\pi}{2}\int_{0}^{\pi&#x2F;2} \frac{\sin x}{1+\cos^2x}$,后面再凑微分即可</p><p>$\int_0^{\pi&#x2F;2} \frac{x}{1+\sin x+\cos x}\overset{t&#x3D;\pi&#x2F;2-x}{&#x3D;} \frac{\pi}{4} \int_0^{\pi&#x2F;2} \frac{1}{1+\sin t+\cos t}dt$,之后用万能公式代换</p></blockquote><p>$\int_0^a \sqrt{a^2-x^2}dx&#x3D;\frac{\pi a^2}{4}$</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
